reviewText: I love this series!  I just wish I could find the third season.  Great premise:  the devil is bored and takes a bet from a soul collector that he cannot redeem the souls of people before their contract times have finished.  Sometimes the collector wins, but at other times the outcome is more frightening.

This tv show is a really good. It has a great premise which is both dark and hopeful at the same time. I really which I could find a way to purchase this season of this show somehow. Amazon please bring this back.
